      "actor": 302080,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "expression": 1,
      "say": "……指挥官，站在原地不要乱动。",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "effects": [
        {
          "name": "speed",
          "active": true
        }
      ],
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_task"
    },
    {
      "say": "否则无法保证你的安全。",
      "actor": 302080,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_task"
    },
    {
      "say": "听到{namecode:181}突如其来的危险预告，全身仿佛连同周围的空气都被一起凝固了。",
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "effects": [
        {
          "name": "speed",
          "active": false
        }
      ],
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_task"
    },
    {
      "say": "这就对了，在我说可以之前就这样站在原地。",
      "actor": 302080,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_task"
    },
    {
      "actor": 302080,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "expression": 2,
      "say": "也不是什么大事，只不过现在有只胡蜂在你衣领上而————不是说了不要动么……",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_task"
    },
    {
      "say": "……冷静下来再坚持一会，我这就去把窗户打开。",
      "actor": 302080,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_task"
    },
    {
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "say": "{namecode:181}冷静的穿过了胡蜂的攻击范围，以最小的动静重新打开了指挥室的窗户。",
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_task"
    },
    {
      "say": "听好，指挥官，强行甩掉胡蜂只会刺激它使用毒刺反击。",
